<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,2007,2032]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Distribution.</emphasis>
The species is recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[689,811,2007,2032]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
